e Americans have won four straight gold medals in the last four Summer Games.\", \"from\": 43691, \"to\": 43770, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 43691, \"end\": 43704, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\", \"score\": 0.999999998230237, \"rank\": 9.414509980063367e-10, \"text\": \"The Americans\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"four straight gold medals\", \"from\": 43714, \"to\": 43739}, {\"ngram\": \"the last four Summer Games\", \"from\": 43743, \"to\": 43769}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fencing is one of the five sports that permanent fixture at theOlympic Gamessince the modern Games inception in 1896.\", \"from\": 43774, \"to\": 43891, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Fencing\", \"from\": 43774, \"to\": 43781}, {\"ngram\": \"the five sports\", \"from\": 43792, \"to\": 43807}, {\"ngram\": \"theOlympic Gamessince\", \"from\": 43834, \"to\": 43855}, {\"ngram\": \"the modern Games inception\", \"from\": 43856, \"to\": 43882}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The lam\\u00e9 is an electrically conductive garment worn over the scoring area for eachfencing sword type.The lam\\u00e9 enables hits to register automatically.\", \"from\": 43893, \"to\": 44042, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The lam\\u00e9\", \"from\": 43893, \"to\": 43901}, {\"ngram\": \"an electrically conductive garment\", \"from\": 43905, \"to\": 43939}, {\"ngram\": \"the scoring area\", \"from\": 43950, \"to\": 43966}, {\"ngram\": \"sword type\", \"from\": 43983, \"to\": 43993}, {\"ngram\": \"The lam\\u00e9\", \"from\": 43994, \"to\": 44002}, {\"ngram\": \"hits\", \"from\": 44011, \"to\": 44015}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The lam\\u00e9 may cover more or less of the body depending on which blade the fencer uses.\", \"from\": 44044, \"to\": 44129, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The lam\\u00e9\", \"from\": 44044, \"to\": 44052}, {\"ngram\": \"the body\", \"from\": 44079, \"to\": 44087}, {\"ngram\": \"the fencer uses\", \"from\": 44113, \"to\": 44128}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are three different kinds of blades used in the modern fencing: foil, \\u00e9p\\u00e9e, and sabre.\", \"from\": 44130, \"to\": 44222, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"three different kinds\", \"from\": 44140, \"to\": 44161}, {\"ngram\": \"blades\", \"from\": 44165, \"to\": 44171}, {\"ngram\": \"the modern fencing\", \"from\": 44180, \"to\": 44198}, {\"ngram\": \"foil\", \"from\": 44200, \"to\": 44204}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e9p\\u00e9e\", \"from\": 44206, \"to\": 44210}, {\"ngram\": \"sabre\", \"from\": 44216, \"to\": 44221}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The foil blade weighs a maximum of 500 grams (1.1 lbs.)\", \"from\": 44224, \"to\": 44279, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The foil blade\", \"from\": 44224, \"to\": 44238}, {\"ngram\": \"a maximum\", \"from\": 44246, \"to\": 44255}, {\"ngram\": \"500 grams\", \"from\": 44259, \"to\": 44268}, {\"ngram\": \"1.1 lbs\", \"from\": 44270, \"to\": 44277}]}, {\"sentence\": \"and is a thrusting weapon.\", \"from\": 44280, \"to\": 44306, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a thrusting weapon\", \"from\": 44287, \"to\": 44305}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When using the foil only the tip of the blade counts with the target area of the torso, which is covered by lam\\u00e9.\", \"from\": 44307, \"to\": 44420, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the foil\", \"from\": 44318, \"to\": 44326}, {\"ngram\": \"only the tip\", \"from\": 44327, \"to\": 44339}, {\"ngram\": \"the blade\", \"from\": 44343, \"to\": 44352}, {\"ngram\": \"the target area\", \"from\": 44365, \"to\": 44380}, {\"ngram\": \"the torso\", \"from\": 44384, \"to\": 44393}, {\"ngram\": \"lam\\u00e9\", \"from\": 44415, \"to\": 44419}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The foil is the most familiar of the three disciplines.\", \"from\": 44422, \"to\": 44477, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The foil\", \"from\": 44422, \"to\": 44430}, {\"ngram\": \"the three disciplines\", \"from\": 44455, \"to\": 44476}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It has the smallest target area and is light, allowing for numerous different attacks.\", \"from\": 44478, \"to\": 44564, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the smallest target area\", \"from\": 44485, \"to\": 44509}, {\"ngram\": \"numerous different attacks\", \"from\": 44537, \"to\": 44563}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The \\u00e9p\\u00e9e is also a thrusting blade but has a maximum weight of 775 grams (1.7 lbs.).\", \"from\": 44566, \"to\": 44650, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The \\u00e9p\\u00e9e\", \"from\": 44566, \"to\": 44574}, {\"ngram\": \"a thrusting blade\", \"from\": 44583, \"to\": 44600}, {\"ngram\": \"a maximum weight\", \"from\": 44609, \"to\": 44625}, {\"ngram\": \"775 grams\", \"from\": 44629, \"to\": 44638}, {\"ngram\": \"1.7 lbs\", \"from\": 44640, \"to\": 44647}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Only the tip of the blade counts when making contact with the opponent, but your own target area is the entire body so there is no lam\\u00e9.\", \"from\": 44651, \"to\": 44787, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Only the tip\", \"from\": 44651, \"to\": 44663}, {\"ngram\": \"the blade\", \"from\": 44667, \"to\": 44676}, {\"ngram\": \"contact\", \"from\": 44696, \"to\": 44703}, {\"ngram\": \"the opponent\", \"from\": 44709, \"to\": 44721}, {\"ngram\": \"your own target area\", \"from\": 44727, \"to\": 44747}, {\"ngram\": \"the entire body\", \"from\": 44751, \"to\": 44766}, {\"ngram\": \"no lam\\u00e9\", \"from\": 44779, \"to\": 44786}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The main differences from the \\u00e9p\\u00e9e and the foil, is that you cannot use the \\\"flick attack\\\" with the \\u00e9p\\u00e9e blade because it is so much heavier.\", \"from\": 44789, \"to\": 44930, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The main differences\", \"from\": 44789, \"to\": 44809}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\u00e9p\\u00e9e\", \"from\": 44815, \"to\": 44823}, {\"ngram\": \"the foil\", \"from\": 44828, \"to\": 44836}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"flick attack\", \"from\": 44861, \"to\": 44878}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\u00e9p\\u00e9e blade\", \"from\": 44885, \"to\": 44899}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The other difference is the whole body is a scoring area.\", \"from\": 44931, \"to\": 44988, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The other difference\", \"from\": 44931, \"to\": 44951}, {\"ngram\": \"the whole body\", \"from\": 44955, \"to\": 44969}, {\"ngram\": \"a scoring area\", \"from\": 44973, \"to\": 44987}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The sabre is a cutting and thrusting weapon with a maximum weight of 500 grams (1.1 lbs.).\", \"from\": 44990, \"to\": 45080, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The sabre\", \"from\": 44990, \"to\": 44999}, {\"ngram\": \"weapon\", \"from\": 45027, \"to\": 45033}, {\"ngram\": \"a maximum weight\", \"from\": 45039, \"to\": 45055}, {\"ngram\": \"500 grams\", \"from\": 45059, \"to\": 45068}, {\"ngram\": \"1.1 lbs\", \"from\": 45070, \"to\": 45077}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The entire blade can be used to score with the target area being the upper half of the body, that includes face mask and neck bib.\", \"from\": 45081, \"to\": 45211, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The entire blade\", \"from\": 45081, \"to\": 45097}, {\"ngram\": \"the target area\", \"from\": 45124, \"to\": 45139}, {\"ngram\": \"the upper half\", \"from\": 45146, \"to\": 45160}, {\"ngram\": \"the body\", \"from\": 45164, \"to\": 45172}, {\"ngram\": \"face mask\", \"from\": 45188, \"to\": 45197}, {\"ngram\": \"neck bib\", \"from\": 45202, \"to\": 45210}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The entire upper half is covered by lam\\u00e9.\", \"from\": 45212, \"to\": 45253, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The entire upper half\", \"from\": 45212, \"to\": 45233}, {\"ngram\": \"lam\\u00e9\", \"from\": 45248, \"to\": 45252}]}, {\"se