ps\", \"from\": 61786, \"to\": 61797}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If you get rid of theOlympic Village, you get rid of a part of the Games,\\\" Henri Specht, the director of the Olympic and Paralympic Village project at SOLIDEO, said, via the IOC.\", \"from\": 61800, \"to\": 61979, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 61922, \"end\": 61940, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paralympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}, {\"begin\": 61975, \"end\": 61978, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9999999993696065, \"rank\": 6.234546507283583e-10, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"theOlympic Village\", \"from\": 61819, \"to\": 61837}, {\"ngram\": \"a part\", \"from\": 61854, \"to\": 61860}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 61864, \"to\": 61873}, {\"ngram\": \"Henri Specht\", \"from\": 61876, \"to\": 61888}, {\"ngram\": \"the director\", \"from\": 61890, \"to\": 61902}, {\"ngram\": \"SOLIDEO\", \"from\": 61952, \"to\": 61959}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's probably the only place and the only time on the planet when you have so many countries coming together at the same location.\", \"from\": 61981, \"to\": 62112, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the only place\", \"from\": 61996, \"to\": 62010}, {\"ngram\": \"the only time\", \"from\": 62015, \"to\": 62028}, {\"ngram\": \"the planet\", \"from\": 62032, \"to\": 62042}, {\"ngram\": \"so many countries\", \"from\": 62057, \"to\": 62074}, {\"ngram\": \"the same location\", \"from\": 62094, \"to\": 62111}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think that every nation is very attached to the Village and the athletes who have in it have come out with a unique life experience.\\\"\", \"from\": 62113, \"to\": 62248, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"every nation\", \"from\": 62126, \"to\": 62138}, {\"ngram\": \"the Village\", \"from\": 62159, \"to\": 62170}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 62175, \"to\": 62187}, {\"ngram\": \"a unique life experience\", \"from\": 62222, \"to\": 62246}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fox News' Ryan Gaydos contributed to this report.\", \"from\": 62250, \"to\": 62299, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 62250, \"end\": 62258, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"score\": 0.9999331457289505, \"rank\": 5.8088165910003906e-05, \"text\": \"Fox News\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\"}, {\"begin\": 62260, \"end\": 62264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.6435321254797679, \"rank\": 0.5537356700669754, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this report\", \"from\": 62287, \"to\": 62298}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic rings are plastered all throughout the world during Olympic times.\", \"from\": 62303, \"to\": 62381, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympic rings\", \"from\": 62303, \"to\": 62320}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 62350, \"to\": 62359}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic times\", \"from\": 62367, \"to\": 62380}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But what do they actually stand for?\", \"from\": 62382, \"to\": 62418, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The logo was designed and hand-drawn in 1913 by Pierre de Coubertin, the founder of the modernOlympic Games.\", \"from\": 62420, \"to\": 62528, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 62468